videos.description: The Raptors' Fred VanVleet throws up a deep 3-pointer that connects to beat the buzzer and end the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (VanVleet’s heave beats the 2nd-quarter buzzer) 2021/3/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: VanVleet's heave beats the 2nd-quarter buzzer

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell scores eight straight points down the stretch as the Jazz fend off the Raptors to become the first team with 30 wins.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell's clutch play sends Jazz to 30th win) 2021/3/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell's clutch play sends Jazz to 30th win
